OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,FEvents leading up to a fatal arson
OL,7,Fattack which claimed the lives of a
OL,8,Fmother and her four children will be
OL,9,Freinvestigated by the police watchdog.
OL,11,FDemi Pearson, 15, her eight-year-old
OL,12,Fbrother Brandon and sisters Lacie,
OL,13,Fseven and Lia, three, died in the
OL,14,Fhouse fire on Jackson Street in
OL,15,FWalkden, Greater Manchester, in
OL,16,FDecember 2017.
OL,18,FTheir mother, Michelle Pearson, 37,
OL,19,Fsuffered extensive burns and "clung on
OL,20,Fto life" until she died 20 months
OL,21,Flater.
