OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,FA full inquest into their deaths will
OL,7,Fnow not place until October 2026, as
OL,8,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,9,FConduct (IOPC) takes a fresh look at
OL,10,Fthe family's prior contact with
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,12,Finvolving incidents and threats from
OL,13,Ftheir killers.
OL,15,FThe original report was completed in
OL,16,F2019 but not made public, although it
OL,17,Fwas shared with GMP, the local coroner
OL,18,Fand members of the Pearson family.
