OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,FGMP later alerted the police watchdog
OL,7,Fregarding "some concerns" over the
OL,8,FIOPC probe and in January this year
OL,9,Fasked the watchdog to review it.
OL,11,FAt a pre-inquest review hearing on
OL,12,FMonday 16 June, Nicholas Flanagan,
OL,13,Frepresenting the IOPC, said a decision
OL,14,Fhad been made to reinvestigate and the
OL,15,F2019 report consequently has "no legal
OL,16,Fstanding".
OL,18,FHe told Bolton Coroner's Court: "This
OL,19,Fis effectively a brand new, fresh
OL,20,Finvestigation into all matters."
