OL,6,FThe first investigation examined the
OL,7,Fcontact between GMP and Ms Pearson and
OL,8,Fher family from 26 November to 11
OL,9,FDecember 2017 ` when the blaze took
OL,10,Fplace in the early hours ` and
OL,11,Fincluded reports to the force about
OL,12,Fproperty being damaged at Ms Pearson's
OL,13,Fhome, and further threats to damage
OL,14,Fthe house.
OL,16,FThe actions of the officers who
OL,17,Fattended the scene of the blaze did
OL,18,Fnot form part of the investigation,
OL,19,Fsaid the IOPC.
