OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,FMs Pearson had "begged" to be rehoused
OL,7,Fand called police on five occasions in
OL,8,Fthe two weeks before the fatal attack,
OL,9,Fthe trial of her killers heard.
OL,11,FAnna Morris, representing the Pearson
OL,12,Ffamily, said the family acknowledged
OL,13,F"with the deepest of frustrations" the
OL,14,Fneed to delay proceedings as they have
OL,15,F"strongly held views about the quality
OL,16,Fof the first investigation".
OL,18,FShe added: "All they have ever wanted
OL,19,Fto know is the truth."
