OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,FA full inquest, scheduled to last up
OL,7,Fto eight weeks, will take place from 5
OL,8,FOctober.
OL,10,FA further pre-inquest review hearing
OL,11,Fon 9 October 2024 was set by Timothy
OL,12,FBrennand, HM Coroner for Manchester
OL,13,FWest.
OL,15,FZak Bolland and David Worrall were
OL,16,Fjailed for life for the murders and
OL,17,Ftold they would serve a minimum of 40
OL,18,Fand 37 years respectively for the
OL,19,Fpetrol bomb attack on the Pearson
OL,20,Ffamily home.
