OL,7,Fwas jailed for 21 years for four
OL,8,Fcounts of manslaughter after the trial
OL,9,Fat Manchester Crown Crown Court.
OL,11,FAll three followed Monday's
OL,12,Fproceedings on remote links from
OL,13,Fcustody.
