OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,FFollowing the hearing, IOPC deputy
OL,7,Fdirector of investigations Catherine
OL,8,FBates said: "The deaths of Michelle
OL,9,FPearson and four of her children were
OL,10,Fa tragedy that has affected so many
OL,11,Fand our thoughts remain with their
OL,12,Ffamily who have endured unimaginable
OL,13,Fsuffering.
OL,15,F"Having carefully considered the
OL,16,Favailable information and comments
OL,17,Ffrom GMP, the coroner and the family,
OL,18,Fwe believe there is a requirement for
OL,19,Fthe IOPC to reopen the investigation.
