OL,3,CRun up to fatal arson attack to be
OL,4,Creinvestigated by police watchdog
OL,6,F"We are extremely conscious of the
OL,7,Fimpact this decision will have on all
OL,8,Fthose involved given the length of
OL,9,Ftime since the attack on the Pearsons'
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,F"We know that it benefits nobody to
OL,13,Fhave key questions unanswered and no
OL,14,Fstone will be left unturned in our
OL,15,Freinvestigation."
OL,17,FA team, with no connection to the
OL,18,Foriginal IOPC investigation, has been
OL,19,Fset up to ensure this investigation is
OL,20,Fcompleted "as quickly and
OL,21,Fproportionately" as possible.
