OL,6,FMs Bates added: "We will ensure the
OL,7,Ffamily and the coroner are kept
OL,8,Fupdated with the progress of the
OL,9,Finvestigation."
OL,11,FThe IOPC added that, as standard in
OL,12,Fsuch probes, the lead investigator
OL,13,Fmust determine whether there is an
OL,14,Findication anyone serving with the
OL,15,Fpolice may have committed a criminal
OL,16,Foffence or behaved in a way that would
OL,17,Fjustify bringing disciplinary
OL,18,Fproceedings.
